title: Gold 2 ADC main LF supp duo (Gold+)

embed.description: Create & discover new Champion builds/strategies, check your Summoner statistics and try our powerful LoL charts.

body:
Hey, I am currently a Gold 2 ADC main, Plat 5 last season, haven't ranked up much this season because I have been focusing on other aspects of my life and what not, but jumping back into it and really would like to have a support duo.

Preferably someone around gold or higher if they are interested, I am available every afternoon and would to duo most days.

Add me if you are interested, lolking to my account was also linked

IGN: Fig
